OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1784225905
OL,3,CFirst lowland tapir calf born in 14
OL,4,Cyears at Hertfordshire Zoo
OL,6,FIt's a special day at a zoo in
OL,7,FHertfordshire celebrating the first
OL,8,Fbirth of its kind for 14 years.
OL,10,FA new lowland tapir calf was born
OL,11,Fafter a 430-day pregnancy.
OL,13,FThey're under pressure in the wild
OL,14,Fbecause of predators, habitat loss and
OL,15,Fslow reproduction rates.
OL,17,FHertfordshire Zoo said the calf, which
OL,18,Fhasn't been named yet, was on his feet
OL,19,Fin ten minutes
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
