OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1784225905
OL,3,CFirst lowland tapir calf born in 14
OL,4,Cyears at Hertfordshire Zoo
OL,6,FLowland tapirs are currently
OL,7,Fclassified as vulnerable on the
OL,8,FInternational Union of Conservation of
OL,9,FNature's Red List, due to
OL,10,Fdeforestation and habitat loss.
OL,12,FWatch: The newborn explores his
OL,13,Fsurroundings at Hertfordshire Zoo.
OL,15,FThe calf's mother is a 20 year old
OL,16,Ftapir, called Fifi who was pregnant
OL,17,Ffor over a year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
