OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1784225905
OL,3,CFirst lowland tapir calf born in 14
OL,4,Cyears at Hertfordshire Zoo
OL,6,FThis is her fourth calf, and the zoo
OL,7,Fsay that both mother and baby are
OL,8,Fdoing exceptionally well, but will be
OL,9,Fkept under close supervision.
OL,11,FTyler Whitnall, Managing Director of
OL,12,FHertfordshire Zoo, said:
OL,14,F"Welcoming our first lowland tapir
OL,15,Fcalf in 14 years is an incredibly
OL,16,Fproud moment for everyone at
OL,17,FHertfordshire Zoo. And Fifi is proving
OL,18,Fto be an exceptional mum already.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
