OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1784225905
OL,3,CFirst lowland tapir calf born in 14
OL,4,Cyears at Hertfordshire Zoo
OL,6,F"This birth represents hope for a
OL,7,Fspecies that is under increasing
OL,8,Fpressure in the wild.
OL,10,F"Hertfordshire Zoo has been a long
OL,11,Fterm supporter of the Lowland Tapir
OL,12,FConservation Initiative, who are
OL,13,Fhelping protect the future of lowland
OL,14,Ftapirs in South America."
OL,16,FNewborn lowland tapirs are born
OL,17,Fcovered in vivid cream stripes and
OL,18,Fspots, this differs completely from
OL,19,Fthe dark grey coats of adults.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
